效，全面拥抱人工智能大潮，借助先进的数字化工具和平台，实现业务流程的自动化、标准化和可视化。名创优品叶国富：严禁一切形式主义"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0116e0bfa2caa8d44348af813ec2570f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/11414052749"}}, "attached_info": "CkII3N6xwIyBjd0NEAMaCTExMzI1ODYxMyCuypC9BjAAOLQBQAVyCzExNDE0MDUyNzQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1738884189.145326", "card_id": "Q_67086259", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么黄帝和蚩尤决战，他把蚩尤给杀了，而和炎帝决战却不杀他？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么黄帝和蚩尤决战，他把蚩尤给杀了，而和炎帝决战却不杀他"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3486ca04ab046b6edd22f6fb14c8b31_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/67086259"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I3N6xwIyBjd0NEAMaCDE5MDYyMzQ3IOHDt88FMAA4dEAGcgg2NzA4NjI1OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1738884189.145573", "card_id": "Q_11167705734", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《黑神话悟空》和《哪吒 2》都出现用下界的妖炼丹的情节，这是中国传统神魔小说里的设定还是哪部作品的独创？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8ade61511366cb78f0a1d93f81